Name: Trapped
About the game: Trapped is an Indie Horror styled Action/adventure puzzle game. In which the player finds themselves trapped in the childhood manor of Aki, the game's young protagonist. Eluding the undead and other monsters while trying to figure out Why Aki was trapped, and how she can escape.
